  <thing id="deiShadow" name="Shadow, The" description="The Shadow, the literal shadow of Aureon, gained a life of its own as the price of his arcane mastery.  Chaotic evil, it devotes its energy to dark magic and the corruption of nature.  Many evil wizards and sorcerers revere the Shadow, and many of the monsters of Droamm invoke its name as well.  It is usually depicted as a shadow dragon.  It is associated with the domains of Chaos, Evil, Magic, and Shadow.  The Shadow&apos;s favored weapon is the quarterstaff." compset="Deity" uniqueness="unique">
    <fieldval field="deiEpithet" value="God of Shadow and Corruption"/>
